<Author>RichiePR77
<Content>The best anniversary at the best place! We came today from a weekend at the Parador Palmas de Luc铆a. Is the best place for a great vacation. All the excellent attention we got and the service was great.The food was the best. We got the All-inclusive package (which, by the way, recommend it), so we didn't worry about nothing. You go to the restaurant, write down the time you want to eat and what you want, you come at that time and give the room number and 5 minutes later... voila! food is at your table. Quality of food is great.You have a room with a small balcony but with a beautiful view. A/C worked great. We had a small glitch with the hot water, but we didn't understand at first, this is a green hotel. It's a solar heater, and the first day it wasn't so hot... but the next two days, it was solved.The pool, albeit small, is was perfect if you want to relax, even enjoy it with your family, The beach near is beautiful.This is a green hotel, so you will se reciclying and reuse tips all over, but it works.Looking forward to come back next year. 
